description: This dashboard shows live load test metrics provided by JMeter.

panels.content: The following panels show aggregated metrics for all requests

targets.query: SELECT last("startedThreads") FROM "virtualUsers" WHERE $timeFilter
SELECT count("responseCode")/$testDuration as "200" FROM "errorsRaw" WHERE  $timeFilter AND ("responseCode" = '200')
SELECT  count("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE $timeFilter
SELECT 1 - sum("errorCount")/count("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE $timeFilter
SELECT sum("errorCount")/count("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE $timeFilter
SELECT sum("errorCount") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE $timeFilter
SELECT mean("meanActiveThreads") FROM "virtualUsers" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s) fill(null)
SELECT  count("responseTime")/$aggregation FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT sum("errorCount") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)

SELECT count("responseCode") as "SocketException" FROM "errorsRaw" WHERE  $timeFilter AND (("responseCode" != '400') AND ("responseCode" != '302') AND ("responseCode" != '500') AND ("responseCode" != '404') AND ("responseCode" != '403') AND ("responseCode" != '503') AND ("responseCode" != '502')  AND ("responseCode" != '200') AND ("responseCode" != '504')) GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseCode") as "200" FROM "errorsRaw" WHERE  $timeFilter AND ("responseCode" = '200')  GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseCode") as "302" FROM "errorsRaw" WHERE  $timeFilter AND ("responseCode" = '302')  GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseCode") as "500" FROM "errorsRaw" WHERE  $timeFilter AND "responseCode" = '500' GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseCode") as "404" FROM "errorsRaw" WHERE  $timeFilter AND ("responseCode" = '404')  GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseCode") as "403" FROM "errorsRaw" WHERE  $timeFilter AND ("responseCode" = '403')  GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseCode") as "503" FROM "errorsRaw" WHERE  $timeFilter AND "responseCode" = '503' GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseCode") as "502" FROM "errorsRaw" WHERE  $timeFilter AND "responseCode" = '502' GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseCode") as "504" FROM "errorsRaw" WHERE  $timeFilter AND "responseCode" = '504' GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseCode") as "400" FROM "errorsRaw" WHERE  $timeFilter AND ("responseCode" = '400')  GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)

SELECT count("responseCode") as "SocketException" FROM "errorsRaw" WHERE  $timeFilter AND (("responseCode" != '400') AND ("responseCode" != '302') AND ("responseCode" != '500') AND ("responseCode" != '404') AND ("responseCode" != '403') AND ("responseCode" != '503') AND ("responseCode" != '502')  AND ("responseCode" != '200') AND ("responseCode" != '504')) GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT mean("sendByte") FROM "connectRaw" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT mean("responseSize") FROM "connectRaw" WHERE $timeFilter  GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT mean("connectTime") FROM "connectRaw" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT mean("latencyTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT max("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT mean("connectTime") FROM "connectRaw" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT mean("startedThreads") FROM "virtualUsers" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT   percentile(responseTime, 90) FROM "requestsRaw"  WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT   percentile(responseTime, 65) FROM "requestsRaw"  WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT   percentile(responseTime, 50) FROM "requestsRaw"  WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)

SELECT count(responseTime) as Count, mean(responseTime)/1000 as Avg, min(responseTime)/1000 as Min, max(responseTime)/1000 as Max, median(responseTime)/1000 as Median, (sum(errorCount)/count(responseTime)) as "Error Rate", sum(errorCount) as "Error Count" FROM "requestsRaw"  WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY requestName

SELECT  stddev(responseTime)/1000 as "std",percentile(responseTime, 50)/1000 as "50%", percentile(responseTime, 85)/1000 as "85%", percentile(responseTime, 90)/1000 as "90%",percentile(responseTime, 95)/1000 as "95%",percentile(responseTime, 99)/1000 as "99%"  FROM "requestsRaw"  WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY requestName

panels.content: The following panels show request-specific metrics for the request "[[request]]"

targets.query: SELECT count("responseTime")/$aggregation FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT  count("responseTime")/$aggregation FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE $timeFilter AND "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT 1 - sum("errorCount")/count("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE $timeFilter AND "requestName" =~ /^$request$/
SELECT sum("errorCount")/count("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE $timeFilter AND "requestName" =~ /^$request$/
SELECT count("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("responseCode")/$testDuration as "200" FROM "errorsRaw" WHERE  $timeFilter AND ("responseCode" = '200')   and  "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter
SELECT mean("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT percentile("responseTime", 90) FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT percentile("responseTime", 95) FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT percentile("responseTime", 99) FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT max("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT sum("errorCount")/$aggregation FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseCode") as "302" FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter AND ("responseCode" = '302')  GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseCode") as "200" FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter AND ("responseCode" = '200')  GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseCode") as "500" FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter AND ("responseCode" = '500') GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseCode") as "503" FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter AND ("responseCode" = '503')  GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseCode") as "502" FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter AND ("responseCode" = '502')  GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseCode") as "504" FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter AND ("responseCode" = '504')  GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseCode") as "404" FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND $timeFilter AND ("responseCode" = '404')  GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
